  "img": "icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Daren Kael was a structural engineer before he was a hero, and it shows — he thinks about load-bearing, about what holds and what breaks. His suit, AEGIS-02, is the heaviest in the Forgeborn arsenal. He is calm in a fight in a way that unnerves opponents, and he hits like a collapsing building. He and Nadia operate with the shorthand of twenty years of partnership; a look between them is a full conversation.</p>",
